The Portuguese artisans of Khepry are the same men and women who work for some of the greatest brands in the world. Their professionalism is deeply rooted in tradition and so they have flourished for generations. Together, we create a shoe with its own identity and design, manufactured with the highest quality, Therefore, comfort is our greatest concern.The traditional construction is combined with our innovative design and bold attitude. Khepry shoes are made thinking about the contemporary man, bold but in a subtle way.You may be leading a startup or running a Fortune 500 company, Khepry shoes make you feel comfortable in any situation, but more than that, they make you feel different and bold.Khepry will be your new ally to find the best, comfortable and stylish luxury shoes. Help us start our first production!            Khepry is concerned about the environmental impact associated with the manufacturing process, activities, products and services. Therefore, Khepry intends to do so in a sustainable way, reconciling its needs for growth and consolidation in the market, with the need to protect the environment.This is why we choose suppliers that share our concern and who, like us, foster a thorough management of the whole process of developing and manufacturing the respective products.Each pair of Khepry shoes is made of genuine leather. The manual process gives each pair their unique characteristics, and undergoes a rigorous inspection to ensure that each shoe is of the highest quality.Our manufacturing process is done manually and constantly supervised. Each shoe has a great precision and know-how to ensure that the result is flawless.  Our business model is disruptive, eliminating middlemen and retailers. Khepry has reshaped the entire development and manufacturing process in order to optimize costs so we can give our financers a new opportunity to purchase high quality products at a more affordable price. ​Luxury, comfort and quality has a place of enormous prominence in our brand. Khepry shoes are bold, flexible and light. We spent a lot of time developing our shoes to make sure we didn’t miss any detail, and of course, we didn’t cut at any expenses.  That’s why all Khepry footwear: 
Are made of genuine leather personally selected; 
Uses a lightweight sole made of recycled tire rubber, which allows easy and effortless movements and greater adhesion to the ground; 
Are made in order to reduce pressure points around the heel and middle of the foot; 
Allows you to relieve stress while walking because all the shoe is cushioned, and with time the cushion adapts to your foot to improve comfort; 
Uses microfiber lining with absorbent properties to absorb sweat;
   At khepry we take very serious the environmental problems, but we also have a promise to you, to present the best products. With that in mind we created a luxurious collection, with minimum impact. This was possible by using recycled wood in the boxes, leather tanned without chemicals, a sole made of recycled tire rubber and making sure that our suppliers follow the same work ethics as we do.To make sure that khepry makes a significant difference in the world we made a partnership with One Tree Planted organization, wich mean that every time you buy our shoes YOU are making a visible and quick difference by planting two trees in an african forest with a high risk of deforestation.Have a look at their project HERE.    Was designed towards the man who looks for a way to make a difference, and uses the best products on the market in a subtle yet fashionable and exquisite way. This collection is divided in two lines, a casual and a sports one, with unique combinations of colors and materials.     Our shoes go far beyond comfort and style.By eliminating middlemen and retailers, we were able to channel resources and produce the highest quality products at a more affordable price. The luxury doesn’t need to be super expensive, but making shoes with the best materials on the market has its price. Khepry is transparent in its decisions, and have the best materials, and the best manufacturers.Our financiers deserve the best and Khepry knows that.That’s why each order is treated as unique, with care and respect, so that when you receive it you could feel how special you are to us.Each package is composed by a wooden box, lined with soft and luxurious velvet. And each shoe is sent inside a bag with double functionality, in addition to protecting the shoe it can still be used to clean it.    Khepry was not created on a whim. It is the product of years of research and training in the footwear sector. The founder, Jorge Silva, has spent the last few years training, researching and working in the shoe industry in Northern Portugal. With a degree in Footwear Design, he devoted all his time to the realization of a dream, using the experience and knowledge acquired, Jorge created Khepry.To ensure that our financers receive a high quality service, Khepry partnered with an experienced logistics and shoe distribution team.We are excited to share our products and our vision with the world!  Khepry shoes are available from sizes 39 to 45 (European size). By the instructions we give, you are able to find  your model and size and, if the size you ordered is not the best, we will exchange it for you (please see the DELIVERY section below for shipping rates and our exchange policy).Measure with a ruler in cm the distance between the toes and the heel of your foot (like the instructions below)​After taking the measurement, see in our table which number corresponds to the length of your foot.  Khepry is an ambitious brand. We make luxury shoes for everyone, with characteristics that you will love. By meeting our financing goals we want to offer more products and more options.Our expansion goal is to start the production of the already created models that will launch the brand's first collection. Help us reach our financing goal so we can show you how much more Khepry has to offer! As soon as the campaign is over, we will have 2-4 weeks to send in the inquiries and get back the necessary information about the models and size of all financing. The faster we get this information, the lower the likelihood of delays!The production can take from 6 to 8 weeks and will be shipped within 4 weeks.  We will do everything in our power to ensure compliance with the schedule. Khepry is a startup and works with very small margins, so we can not avoid the shipping costs. The cost of international shipments will depend on the destination. Orders shipped within the EU will not incur customs duties, but will be subject to VAT (value added tax). If necessary, local duties and taxes will be charged by the competent authority in the country of destination. (Please determine these charges locally.) QUALITYWe have spent a lot of time looking for the best suppliers and manufacturers in Portugal, who have the best materials, the best facilities and most importantly, the experience to create a luxury shoe worldwide. We didn’t skip any expenses to ensure you will get the best product possible. ACCESSIBILITYBy implementing a disruptive business model that delivers your shoes directly from the artisan's hand to your door, we have eliminated the need for tenants and other intermediaries. The finish and luxury that you will experience with our shoes is unparalleled. We did this for you. COMMUNICATION Your commitment to us is the beginning of a long and beautiful relationship. Khepry is committed to you. We will maintain our strong relationship, offer incredible products and communicate with you at every step of the way. If you have any questions, please contact us at any time! CONSISTENCYEach Khepry shoe is handmade, meaning that there will never be two pairs looking exactly the same. However, each pair goes through a thorough inspection process to ensure the quality you expect from a luxury brand globally is present. EXPERIENCE AND CONFIDENCEWe don’t promise what we can’t keep. We have the infrastructures to guarantee a quiet process, from the order to the delivery. We want to be your go-to brand,and we hope to gain your trust. We are building more than a shoe, we are building a family. The Khepry Family! YOU are essential to the success of our campaign and ultimately to our company. Without you we have no reason to exist. We need your support to get us off the ground and ensure that modern men everywhere have access to Portuguese luxury shoes!Be a part of our group of friends and help us by sharing our campaign with YOUR group of friends.
